h","format-standard","hentry","category-righteousness-al-birr","tag-agreed-upon-muttafaqun-alayhi","tag-family-ties-silat-rahim","tag-kindness-al-latf","tag-life-al-hiyah","tag-manners-adab","tag-parents-walidayn","tag-providence-al-qada-wal-qadr","tag-provision-al-rizq","tag-reward-al-ajr","tag-wealth-al-mal"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-1Xz","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":1089,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/11\/05\/dua-zuhd-basic-needs\/","url_meta":{"origin":7537,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Zuhd: The Prophet supplicates only for basic needs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 5, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, make provision for the family of Muhammad sufficiently nourishing.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6460, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1055 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim Ibn Battal said, \"This narration is evidence for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7844,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/06\/no-hasad-but-two-cases\/","url_meta":{"origin":7537,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Admiration: No envy except for charity, knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no envy but in two cases: a man whom Allah has given wealth and he spends it rightly, and a man whom Allah has given wisdom and he judges and teaches with it.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15292,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/extravagance-gold-silver-silk\/","url_meta":{"origin":7537,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Luxury: Prohibition of silk clothes, gold dishes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Do not drink from gold or silver vessels, and do not wear silk or brocade. Verily, these are for unbelievers in the world and for us in the Hereafter.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5633, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2067 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":640,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/03\/19\/be-determined-in-your-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":7537,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Be determined, certain in your supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 19, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\u201cWhen one of you calls upon Allah, let him be determined in the supplication and he should not say, 'O Allah, give me if You will,' for there is no one to coerce Allah.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38520,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/12\/14\/fate-decreed-womb\/","url_meta":{"origin":7537,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: Destiny decreed while in the mother\u2019s womb","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah has appointed an angel over every womb. He says: O Lord, a drop! O Lord, a clot! O Lord, a bit of flesh! Then if Allah decrees the completion of its creation, he says: O Lord,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32911,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/27\/allah-forgives-man-road\/","url_meta":{"origin":7537,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Roads: Allah forgives man for clearing the street","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhile a man was walking in the road, he found a thorny branch in the road so he moved it aside. Allah appreciated his deed and forgave him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2472, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1914 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","